GIF Forge
===========

Development

  Juan de la Cruz García <delacruzgarciajuan@gmail.com>


Based on Peek
=============

GIF Forge began as a ground-up Python/GTK4 rewrite of Peek, the screen
recorder by Philipp Wolfer (https://github.com/phw/peek). It builds on parts of
Peek's packaging and ffmpeg/gifski encoding knowledge under the
GPL-3.0-or-later license.

Original Peek development

  Philipp Wolfer <ph.wolfer@gmail.com>
  Alessandro Toia <gort818@gmail.com>

Peek was translated by many contributors; see the original project's AUTHORS
file at https://github.com/phw/peek for the full list of translators.
